---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import avatarImg from '../assets/avatar.jpg';
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---

<MainLayout title="About | Steve Frost" description="About Steve Frost - software engineer at Shopify, cyclist, and tree hugger based in Ann Arbor, MI.">
  <section class="py-8">
    <h1 class="sr-only">About</h1>

    <div class="flex flex-col gap-8 md:flex-row md:gap-16">
      <div class="shrink-0 flex justify-center md:justify-start animate-slide-up">
        <div class="group relative inline-block">
          <div class="absolute -inset-2 mask-blob bg-gradient-to-br from-coral-400/30 via-coral-300/30 to-amber-400/30 opacity-0 blur-lg transition-opacity group-hover:opacity-100"></div>
          <Image
            src={avatarImg}
            alt="Steve Frost"
            width={200}
            height={200}
            format="webp"
            quality={80}
            loading="lazy"
            decoding="async"
            class="relative mask-blob border-2 border-white/10 transition-transform group-hover:scale-[1.02]"
          />
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="max-w-2xl space-y-5 text-ctp-subtext0 leading-relaxed animate-fade-in">
        <p>
          I've been tinkering with computers for as long as I can rememberâ€”building rigs for friends,
          throwing together websites for local shops, and definitely getting busted sneaking onto
          the family computer way past bedtime.
        </p>
        <p>
          So naturally, I turned the obsession into a career. I went through the Full-Stack Development
          program at <span class="text-coral-400">Flatiron School</span>, where I learned to think
          more clearly about code, got to build things that actually excited me, and made some
          lifelong friends along the way.
        </p>
        <p>
          These days I'm a software engineer at <span class="text-emerald-400 font-semibold">Shopify</span>,
          where I help build the tools that millions of merchants rely on every day. I care a lot about
          making the web fast, accessible, and a little more open source than I found it.
        </p>
        <p>
          When I close the laptop, you'll probably find me
          <span class="text-coral-300">pedaling around Ann Arbor</span> or
          <span class="text-amber-400">volunteering</span> wherever I can be useful.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Divider -->
    <div class="mx-auto my-16 h-px w-2/3 bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-coral-400/30 to-transparent" aria-hidden="true"></div>

    <div class="text-center md:text-left">
      <h2 class="mb-6 text-xl font-bold text-white">Get in Touch</h2>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-3 md:justify-start">
        <a
          href="https://github.com/steveafrost"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="group inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-white/10 bg-ctp-surface0/50 px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-medium text-ctp-subtext1 backdrop-blur transition-all hover:scale-105 hover:border-coral-400/30 hover:text-white active:scale-95"
        >
          <svg class="h-5 w-5 transition-transform group-hover:rotate-12" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M12 2C6.477 2 2 6.484 2 12.017c0 4.425 2.865 8.18 6.839 9.504.5.092.682-.217.682-.483 0-.237-.008-.868-.013-1.703-2.782.605-3.369-1.343-3.369-1.343-.454-1.158-1.11-1.466-1.11-1.466-.908-.62.069-.608.069-.608 1.003.07 1.531 1.032 1.531 1.032.892 1.53 2.341 1.088 2.91.832.092-.647.35-1.088.636-1.338-2.22-.253-4.555-1.113-4.555-4.951 0-1.093.39-1.988 1.029-2.688-.103-.253-.446-1.272.098-2.65 0 0 .84-.27 2.75 1.026A9.564 9.564 0 0112 6.844c.85.004 1.705.115 2.504.337 1.909-1.296 2.747-1.027 2.747-1.027.546 1.379.202 2.398.1 2.651.64.7 1.028 1.595 1.028 2.688 0 3.848-2.339 4.695-4.566 4.943.359.309.678.92.678 1.855 0 1.338-.012 2.419-.012 2.747 0 .268.18.58.688.482A10.019 10.019 0 0022 12.017C22 6.484 17.522 2 12 2z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
          </svg>
          GitHub
        </a>
        <a
          href="mailto:hello@steveafrost.com"
          class="group inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-white/10 bg-ctp-surface0/50 px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-medium text-ctp-subtext1 backdrop-blur transition-all hover:scale-105 hover:border-amber-400/30 hover:text-white active:scale-95"
        >
          <svg class="h-5 w-5 transition-transform group-hover:-rotate-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M21.75 6.75v10.5a2.25 2.25 0 01-2.25 2.25h-15a2.25 2.25 0 01-2.25-2.25V6.75m19.5 0A2.25 2.25 0 0019.5 4.5h-15a2.25 2.25 0 00-2.25 2.25m19.5 0v.243a2.25 2.25 0 01-1.07 1.916l-7.5 4.615a2.25 2.25 0 01-2.36 0L3.32 8.91a2.25 2.25 0 01-1.07-1.916V6.75" />
          </svg>
          Email
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</MainLayout>
